Dia membuktikan nilainya sekali lagi.

44
00:04:05,110 --> 00:04:06,030
Sekali lagi.

45
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,930
Awak semua, saya...

46
00:04:08,010 --> 00:04:11,360
Hidup ini pasti mudah saja bagi dia.

47
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:15,410
Dia kacak, popular dan kaya.

48
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:18,880
Tiada apa nak dirisaukan, bukan?

49
00:04:19,370 --> 00:04:21,079
Dia patut dimarahi
kalau ada yang dia risau.

50
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:23,990
Tapi tak bosankah
kalau hidup tanpa risaukan apa-apa?

51
00:04:25,530 --> 00:04:27,420
Mari kita minum. Minum!

52
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,350
- Minum.
- Minum!

53
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,340
Boleh awak bangun?

54
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,280
Ambillah.

55
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,740
Memalukannya.

56
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,770
Kenapa?

57
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:53,330
Tak ada apa-apa.

58
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:55,880
Tentu saya mengeluh terlalu kuat.

59
